des:
100.7 THE FOUNDRY is Waupaca’s exclusive “ROCK” Station. 100.7 THE FOUNDRY plays rock hits from the mid-1970s to the early 1990s, with music from the 1980s serving as the core of our format. 

70's ARTISTS: Led Zeppelin, Black Sabbath, Aerosmith, Van Halen, Rush & More

80's ARTISTS: Motley Crue, Great White, Tesla, Guns N Roses, Poison, Twisted Sister

90's ARTISTS: Nirvana, Stone Temple Pilots, Metallica, Danzig, Foo Fighters, Bush
